How to set up and run the project:-

install docker composer and docker
=================================
Go to the following page and do the steps:-
https://linuxize.com/post/how-to-install-and-use-docker-compose-on-ubuntu-18-04/

install docker :-
Go to the below url and do the steps:-
https://docs.docker.com/install/linux/docker-ce/ubuntu/


clone the files fom git respository
====================================
git clone https://github.com/shogunjames/coding-challenge.git

Running the project:-
=========================
run the following command :-
 sudo docker-compose up


Take the url :-
http://localhost:8080/

To import database and tables
===================================
sudo docker exec -it php_api bash

php bin/console make:migration

php bin/console doctrine:migrations:migrate

php bin/console doctrine:schema:update --force

I have uploaded a video of my working code challenge work here:-

https://github.com/shogunjames/coding-challenge/blob/master/working demo.mkv

